# Bubble Pop (Bubble Shooter) — stable v1

`bubble-pop` is tagged `stable: 'v1'` in `src/platform/catalog.ts`. See `STABLE.md`.

## Do not change

Unless the user **explicitly authorizes** changes to Bubble Pop:

- Do not edit files under `src/games/bubble-pop/` or `games/bubble-pop/`
- Do not change bubble launch physics, matching/clearing logic, grid layout, scoring, level progression, or difficulty
- Do not change premium presentation (UI, graphics, audio, effects, HUD, menus) without authorization

## Frozen scope

- `src/games/bubble-pop/game.ts` — gameplay logic
- `src/games/bubble-pop/main.ts` — bootstrap, HUD wiring
- `src/games/bubble-pop/bpAudio.ts` — arcade SFX
- `src/games/bubble-pop/bpRender.ts` — premium canvas rendering
- `src/games/bubble-pop/bpEffects.ts` — float text, combos, particles
- `src/games/bubble-pop/style.css` — theme and shell chrome
- `games/bubble-pop/index.html` — menus, HUD, overlays

## Instead

- Copy Bubble Pop **patterns** into shared modules or other games
- Fix platform/hub/backend issues without touching Bubble Pop game code
- If a shared change affects Bubble Pop, **tell the user** which shared file changed and why
